  "body": "<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595892368107-A520VHYPOGZ97PRWHFY5/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>A couple months ago we threw our friend Christina a baby sprinkle at my house. It was such a fun and sweet celebration for this mama of twin boys to help welcome a third little guy into their lives. It was a casual Thursday brunch and these photos were taken by our friend, Flora. Even though we have a separate playroom for the kids, you might notice none of these photos were actually even taken in that room. Toys were all over the living room and in the backyard!</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"13b-image.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595892420207-94Z67MFJI2KPFCRNPORP/13b-image.jpg\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"13c-image.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595892419456-48K5Z0NDHJM13FSN11YR/13c-image.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"13d-image.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595892493628-GFKBXRIM5XE049TMN6MS/13d-image.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"13f-image.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595892511239-XQH2DQ56WKG498KMP5Q6/13f-image.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"13g-image.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595892514207-BZKYBJT4CR9Z6Y8XMU8Z/13g-image.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"13e-image.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595892494158-UG971DVA76TXX9O7GRVT/13e-image.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"13h-image.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595892533640-SZSIJDQQOLCLRO0VE9X7/13h-image.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"13i-image.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595892537735-GK3ZBQ8L7G2F5SCX931R/13i-image.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"13j-image.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595892559751-F4CSRAZ93Z0PQF0QXKZD/13j-image.jpg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>Jack's known many of these kids since he was just weeks old, so it's been really fun watching them all grow up. We had a ball!</p>"
